                "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
              },
              "displayName": "Alejandro Abdelnur",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Europe/Madrid"
            },
            "body": "Daryn, apologies, didn't mean to confuse you, 6 months is 'reasonable' expiration time most countries ask when you enter the country. Reasonable in this case would be a few hours if not several minutes.",
